{"id":232178385,"title":"[開箱]客氣·客器濾杯","content":"相信有些愛好kono濾杯的人\n喜歡層次分明的口感 \n可是偏偏是塑膠製品 不耐用 有健康疑慮啊\n當它裂開時 我整個就不爽了\n於是～現煮時 包軌～\nhttps://i.imgur.com/kcSRfSW.jpg\n驗明正身 客家本色 樸實無華的包裝\nhttps://i.imgur.com/4gJzyUR.jpg\n恰如其分的外盒\nhttps://i.imgur.com/O9VyYM7.jpg\n類似kono的溝槽\n美的不要不要的 喜歡藍色的憂鬱 \n在燈光下閃爍著光芒\n在口感上 帶有陶瓷堅毅的口感\n比kono稍微厚實 屬於口感加強版\n流速也比kono慢 沖煮時要有耐心\n有時用一次不習慣\n用了五次就會習慣\n但是說了這麼多優點 難道沒有缺點嗎？\n當然還是有 一個濾杯1350+運費60\n總共1410元 不是每個人都願意花這麼高的單價\n買一個濾杯\n但看著它宛如藝術品的當下 \n一切都值得了😳","excerpt":"相信有些愛好kono濾杯的人，喜歡層次分明的口感，可是偏偏是塑膠製品 不耐用 有健康疑慮啊，當它裂開時 我整個就不爽了，於是～現煮時 包軌～驗明正身 客家本色 樸實無華的包裝，恰如其分的外盒，類似ko","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"6120536f-6a70-49bb-8891-ec0ba2f4b396","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-09-27T04:22:04.224Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-27T04:23:40.499Z","commentCount":11,"likeCount":13,"tags":[],"topics":["咖啡","手沖咖啡"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"咖啡","forumAlias":"coffee","school":"大葉大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":13}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/kcSRfSW.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/4gJzyUR.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/O9VyYM7.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"a9d6d2a3-6952-41ab-b4ed-1159dae291a6","url":"https://i.imgur.com/kcSRfSWl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/kcSRfSWl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/kcSRfSWl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-27T04:22:04.224Z","updatedAt":"2019-09-27T04:23:40.499Z"},{"id":"a9d6d2a3-6952-41ab-b4ed-1159dae291a6","url":"https://i.imgur.com/kcSRfSW.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/kcSRfSW","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/kcSRfSWl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-09-27T04:22:0